      <title>日本功能失调的债券市场显示出更多复苏迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/japan-s-dysfunctional-bond-market-shows-more-signs-of-recovery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行的一项调查显示，日本债券市场出现了更多持续改善的迹象，尽管十多年来激进的货币宽松政策降低了投资者积极交易的动力，但日本债券市场仍然运转不良。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-03/japan-s-dysfunctional-bond-market-shows-more-signs-of-recovery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 06:42:56 GMT</pubDate>
